                            <html:h1 class="title">Widgets Tutorial - Child Widgets</html:h1>
                            <html:span class="subtitle"></html:span>
                            <!-- $$$tutorials/widgets/childwidget-description -->
                            <html:div class="descr">
                                <html:a name="details"></html:a>
                                <html:p>We can add a child widget to the window created in the
                                    previous example by passing <html:code>window</html:code> as the
                                    parent to its constructor. In this case, we add a button to the
                                    window and place it in a specific location:</html:p>
                                <html:div class="qt-code"><html:div class="table"><html:table
                                            class="generic">
                                            <html:tbody>
                                                <html:tr class="odd" valign="top">
                                                  <html:td><html:pre class="cpp"><html:span
                                                  class="preprocessor">#include
                                                  &lt;QtWidgets&gt;</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="type">int</html:span>
                                                  main(<html:span class="type">int</html:span>
                                                  argc<html:span class="operator">,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="type">char</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="operator"
                                                  >*</html:span>argv<html:span class="operator"
                                                  >[</html:span><html:span class="operator"
                                                  >]</html:span>) { <html:span class="type"><html:a
                                                  href="qapplication.html"
                                                  >QApplication</html:a></html:span>
                                                  app(argc<html:span class="operator">,</html:span>
                                                  argv); <html:span class="type"><html:a
                                                  href="qwidget.html">QWidget</html:a></html:span>
                                                  window; window<html:span class="operator"
                                                  >.</html:span>resize(<html:span class="number"
                                                  >320</html:span><html:span class="operator"
                                                  >,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="number">240</html:span>);
                                                  window<html:span class="operator"
                                                  >.</html:span>setWindowTitle(<html:span
                                                  class="type"><html:a href="qapplication.html"
                                                  >QApplication</html:a></html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator"
                                                  >::</html:span>translate(<html:span class="string"
                                                  >"childwidget"</html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator">,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="string">"Child
                                                  widget"</html:span>)); window<html:span
                                                  class="operator">.</html:span>show(); <html:span
                                                  class="type"><html:a href="qpushbutton.html"
                                                  >QPushButton</html:a></html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="operator">*</html:span>button
                                                  <html:span class="operator">=</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="keyword">new</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="type"><html:a
                                                  href="qpushbutton.html"
                                                  >QPushButton</html:a></html:span>( <html:span
                                                  class="type"><html:a href="qapplication.html"
                                                  >QApplication</html:a></html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator"
                                                  >::</html:span>translate(<html:span class="string"
                                                  >"childwidget"</html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator">,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="string">"Press
                                                  me"</html:span>)<html:span class="operator"
                                                  >,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="operator"
                                                  >&amp;</html:span>window); button<html:span
                                                  class="operator">-</html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator">&gt;</html:span>move(<html:span
                                                  class="number">100</html:span><html:span
                                                  class="operator">,</html:span>
                                                  <html:span class="number">100</html:span>);
                                                  button<html:span class="operator"
                                                  >-</html:span><html:span class="operator"
                                                  >&gt;</html:span>show(); <html:span
                                                  class="keyword">return</html:span> app<html:span
                                                  class="operator">.</html:span>exec(); }</html:pre>
                                                  </html:td>
                                                  <html:td><html:img alt=""
                                                  src="images/widgets-tutorial-childwidget.png"
                                                   /></html:td>
                                                </html:tr>
                                            </html:tbody>
                                        </html:table></html:div>
                                </html:div><html:p>The button is now a child of the window and will
                                    be deleted when the window is destroyed. Note that hiding or
                                    closing the window does not automatically destroy it. It will be
                                    destroyed when the example exits.</html:p>
